    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in museum-quality condition. This specimen features the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and dual VANOS, delivering power through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. Mechanically optimized with documented rod bearing replacement, subframe reinforcement, and a complete VANOS overhaul. The chassis is laser-straight, utilizing a variable M-differential lock for superior lateral dynamics. Finished in Titanium Silver over Black Nappa leather, the exterior retains its factory depth with no paint correction required. This is a turn-key, investment-grade icon with a pristine maintenance pedigree.",
