      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with this absolute gem of a car, and let me tell you, it's basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It has been pampered since day one\u2014spotless interior, gleaming paint, and it drives like a total dream. If you've been looking for that perfect ride that feels brand new, you've found it. I've taken such good care of it, and I'm sure you're going to love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
