      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered legend. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six delivers razor-sharp throttle response via its six individual throttle bodies, pulling linearly to an 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach: the dual-VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to ensure structural rigidity. Power is managed through a precise 6-speed manual transmission and delivered to the asphalt via the M Variable Differential Lock. With zero deferred maintenance and a chassis that remains as taut as the day it left Regensburg, this is a true collector-grade specimen.",
